{
  "stem": "27443.5",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After a few days, being in Lodz with my girlfriend, I persuaded my friend-- my mother's friend who was from [NON-ENGLISH], and he was carrying a shotgun.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had authority for the Jewish [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I persuaded him that I want to go home to my apartment from where I came from, where I lived before the war.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But my friend was very skeptical that I should go alone, because when I came to Lodz, the Poles were as cruel to Jews the same way as they were before the war.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "For instance, when I was liberated, I had no birth certificate.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I figured when I am home I will go to the magistrate, to have my birth certificate that I should have for the future.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "To have my birth certificate, I had to go back to my house, to go to the janitor that they had the ledger of all the occupants from the building.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I came to my court where I used to live.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And instead to go into the basement where the janitor used to live, now he lived in one of the most prominent Jewish homes in an apartment that the most prominent, most wealthy Jew from the whole court used to live.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I came into his apartment.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told him who I am, and he said-- looked at me, and he says, [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You are still alive?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I disregarded it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he asked me what I want.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I told him what I am looking for.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And sure enough, he pulled out a ledger.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I found in the ledger my whole family, the names.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I got what I needed.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
